{"tid":1195134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國愚(發大財)回應香港100萬人上街反送支: 我不知道，我不曉得","createTime":"2019-06-09T14:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T14:15:14.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b60e760f7c958d3181d5c3b8ca8fc7d9d5970d20","tid":1195134,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=553164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D553164&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq43ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=a8eaa9c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D553164&h=536cc00c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=553164</a><br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜9日率高雄市政府首長，參與高雄龍舟大賽，不過該組共四隊一同競賽，市府隊獲得第三名成績，韓國瑜笑稱「市府年紀偏高」，志在參與希望大家玩得開心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不過面對媒體詢問香港「反送中條款遊行」看法，韓國瑜竟連回稱「我不知道，我不曉得」</strong>，針對未來韓粉團體將以「一週一造勢」模式舉辦韓國瑜造勢大會，韓國瑜表示「都是被邀請參加，時間允許都會過去，但不會影響上班時間」。部分網友質疑說「花蓮造勢湧15萬人說法是膨風」，韓國瑜表示「我不知道，但人真的滿多的」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，面對國民黨立委陳宜民指稱，韓國瑜大選勝選後，連一聲感謝都沒有，讓他有些微詞，韓國瑜回應「這是感受問題，很主觀的，也許我謝的不夠，這我要檢討」，但韓國瑜也指出「其實我謝幾十次了，當面看到都有說謝謝，發LINE或電話都有表達謝意」。"},{"pid":"d27caefc8a2fb3889959ea77a12dc3dfc38852b8","tid":1195134,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZpVb5y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZpVb5y.jpg&h=fc01c1ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"329b141b46d50e5c903d99e534a68f5dddac8f68","tid":1195134,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"支持韓國瑜，支持韓總<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HDi6jGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHDi6jGy.jpg&h=26fdf5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ankxCq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FankxCq3.jpg&h=f2d5bc80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sV2NEo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsV2NEo9.jpg&h=b1a26ead&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}